{"pageProps":{"data":{"contentHtml":"<h4 id=\"bloonstd6-mod-helper\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#bloonstd6-mod-helper\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><a href=\"README\" title=\"README\">BloonsTD6 Mod Helper</a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"btd_mod_helperapiui\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#btd_mod_helperapiui\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><a href=\"README#BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.UI\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.UI\">BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.UI</a></h3>\n<h2 id=\"modpopupimage-class\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#modpopupimage-class\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>ModPopupImage Class</h2>\n<p>Registers an image that can be used within hint / event popups</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-csharp\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">abstract</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">ModPopupImage</span> : <span class=\"hljs-title\">BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModContent</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Inheritance <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/System.Object\" title=\"System.Object\">System.Object</a>  <a href=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModContent\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModContent\">ModContent</a>  ModPopupImage</p>\n<h3 id=\"properties\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#properties\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Properties</h3>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.UI.ModPopupImage.Image\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"modpopupimageimage-property\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#modpopupimageimage-property\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>ModPopupImage.Image Property</h2>\n<p>The Image to use<br>\n<br><br>\n(Name of .png or .jpg, not including file extension)</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-csharp\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public<